layout: post
title: "enabling minimize/maximize button on gnome3"
date: 2011-12-11T00:21:00-08:00
comments: false
---
<div  class=post>
  gconftool-2 --set /desktop/gnome/shell/windows/button_layout --type string close,minimize,maximize: <br> <br>
  or use gconf-editor.which ever you like.  <br> <br>
  Logout->Login, there you have it.  <br>
  BTW, if you want the buttons on the right top,the right string is ":close,minimize,maximize".  <br> <br> <br>
</div>
